{"tid":1253184,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[做實事] 為2019年區議會努力!","createTime":"2019-06-23T12:16:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T15:08:36.000Z","uid":260029,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dab9c419f4ba730b61271b05daaed8f04f151388","tid":1253184,"uid":260029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:16:39.000Z","msg":"已經有大量巴絲為正在發生嘅事情同G20努力.<br />\n應該要有少少事後準備, 以免整個運動(甚至可以話係改革)無以為繼.<br />\n<br />\n依家下下打擊對家有頭有面嘅人嘅做法只能治標, 治本方法一定係由低做起. (拉登死咗咁多年, 中東咪一樣又係七國咁亂, 因為佢地區工作同教育做得好).<br />\n點由低做起, 就係區議會. 建制點解咁多鐵票, 咁多基層支持, 當然蛇齋餅糉同老人院有佢嘅功能; 另外就係地區工作, 點先做到地區工作呢? 扶阿婆過馬路? 錯, 係入區議會! 其實全部都係power paly, 全部都係少數服從多數(民主嘛), 但點解成日好似民意同決策都唔係同一方向呢. 因為議會內嘅民意同社會嘅民意唔一樣囉. 好似鉛水事件, 明明係各區區議員都有責任去搵問題源頭(各區抽樣test, 如果區區都係就即係水源/濾水廠問題, 唔係我哋自己買試紙去test, 自己買濾機去濾).<br />\n<br />\n所以我哋除咗要民意入立法會, 同時要入埋區議會!<br />\n<br />\n但我相信好多市民同我一樣, 根本唔知邊個打邊個, 邊個先揀得過.<br />\n所以我希望有能力巴絲(sorry, 我得idea, 落手落腳唔太識, 但幫到一定幫)可以整個app.<br />\n唔需要好複雜<br />\n<br />\n (1st Layer) 用返23個分區(如下圖)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eac.hk/pdf/distco/2019dc/final/map_dc2019x_index.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eac.hk%2Fpdf%2Fdistco%2F2019dc%2Ffinal%2Fmap_dc2019x_index.pdf&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr17tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=09869a45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eac.hk/pdf/distco/2019dc/final/map_dc2019x_index.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eac.hk/ch/distco/2019dc_elect_map.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eac.hk%2Fch%2Fdistco%2F2019dc_elect_map.htm&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr17tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=d1e980cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eac.hk/ch/distco/2019dc_elect_map.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n(2nd Layer) click入唔同分區可以睇到果區侯選人清單, 簡單show名, 政黨, 號碼<br />\n<br />\n(3rd Layer) 再click候選人名就去到候選人資歷, 如: 名, 政黨, 政積, 出席會議次數, 重大社會議題立場, 甚至可以有個可以即時search該候選人嘅新聞(用外部連結).<br />\n<br />\n咁樣可以方便大家去比較判斷投邊個, 同埋支那點解要網絡長城要鎖國, 因為佢最怕資訊流通! 咁樣佢哋嘅大話就無所遁形! 所以如果個app整得到, &quot;重大社會議題立場&quot;果part應該要有個notice叫牆頭草. 等大家知道佢係政治投機者, 唔係真心服務市民.<br />\n<br />\n如果呢壇嘢成事, 立法會選舉可以照copy, 我相信資訊愈清晰, 市民大眾愈知道點做決定."},{"pid":"0760c6a3f68f481bb84fb8eba8fffa6261551377","tid":1253184,"uid":35842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:17:22.000Z","msg":"[本地]星期三(26號）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XXpnoGr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXXpnoGr.png&h=3d7a1665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zAoZ8Qc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzAoZ8Qc.png&h=f0dedb4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[澳洲 ~ Melb]星期三(26號）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ffqedhH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FffqedhH.png&h=a989d4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTG公海gp: <a href=\"https://t.me/g20helphk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fg20helphk&d=Y7KpFbDUA2jerjE4fgLr17tp0LkHB2EL0pKzUaHUqTQ%3D&h=eaa20179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/g20helphk</a>"},{"pid":"029abbd219e8194b3643bba08a586547a88159e9","tid":1253184,"uid":260029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:18:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c6d83650efb3c568b47ca4a74defba249a8e416a","tid":1253184,"uid":260029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:22:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a70ae2f1984e67cbd8af65daff376f7ec6b966ed","tid":1253184,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8fc5b4956fee6ed63406574024c9715cc2b6acb","tid":1253184,"uid":260029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:32:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"168bff0c209de125f854055db4623c47e1c320f2","tid":1253184,"uid":52200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T12:38:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4e42c84fc71dab832b20cce190b245b9d9c92a7","tid":1253184,"u